    # "For now, I should go see Nora."
    "Por agora, tenho de ir ver a Nora."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:6
translate portuguese u20k_4d7966b5:

    # "I drive to Nora's house and ring her doorbell."
    "Conduzo até à casa da Nora e toco à campainha."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:7
translate portuguese u20k_4238613f:

    # "It's late, but I have to see her, and I think she'll want to see me."
    "Já é tarde, mas tenho de a ver, e acho que ela vai querer ver-me."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:11
translate portuguese u20k_69b62070:

    # "After a few moments, I hear her running down the stairs, then she answers the door."
    "Passados alguns instantes, ouço-a a descer as escadas a correr e, em seguida, ela abre a porta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:12
translate portuguese u20k_f8d211b5:

    # sst "Holy shit, [pcname]! You're back!"
    sst "Caramba, [pcname]! Estás de volta!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:15
translate portuguese u20k_eccf68ff:

    # sst "I thought that stupid machine killed you!"
    sst "Pensei que aquela máquina estúpida te tivesse matado!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:16
translate portuguese u20k_ee6c5ba9:

    # sst "I was going to the police tomorrow to tell them everything!"
    sst "Ia à polícia amanhã para lhes contar tudo!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:17
translate portuguese u20k_0ea0e7d1:

    # sst "Whitney's been talking me out of it for days."
    sst "A Whitney tem-me tentado dissuadir há dias."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:20
translate portuguese u20k_65904dc5:

    # sst "What the hell happened? What was all that shit?"
    sst "Que raio aconteceu? O que foi toda aquela merda?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:21
translate portuguese u20k_04446d5f:

    # pc "I'll tell you all about it tomorrow, but yeah... I went to another world and saw my dad."
    pc "Conto-te tudo amanhã, mas sim... fui para outro mundo e vi o meu pai."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:22
translate portuguese u20k_641bbc8f:

    # sst "That's ridiculous. So fucking stupid."
    sst "Isso é ridículo. Tão estúpido."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:25
translate portuguese u20k_f6493f5d:

    # sst "But, whatever! I'm just glad you're back."
    sst "Mas, tanto faz! Só estou feliz por estares de volta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:26
translate portuguese u20k_fc4e92ee:

    # sst "You look and smell like you crawled out of a dumpster, but you're back!"
    sst "Pareces e cheiras como se tivesses saído de um contentor do lixo, mas estás de volta!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:29
translate portuguese u20k_e5a41f4c:

    # sst "Damn I missed you."
    sst "Raios, senti a tua falta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20k.rpy:30
translate portuguese u20k_919f8db7:

    # sst "Come on... let's take a shower and get in bed."
    sst "Vá lá... vamos tomar um banho e ir para a cama."

